u, and run your hedge fund themselves. And, really, why not? One complaint =
people sometimes have about activist hedge fund managers=C2=A0is that they =
tell companies what to do but don=E2=80=99t themselves have deep experience=
 running those companies, but surely Weinstein and Ackman and Lasry=C2=A0<e=
m>do=C2=A0</em>have lots of experience running hedge funds.</p>
