<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is a traditional way to read this story.=
 The traditional story goes like this:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Jimmy Levin, Sculptor=E2=80=99s CEO, w=
ould like to continue running his hedge fund, and the board, which consists=
