ugh at a reduced salary).</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">And it d=
id not really=C2=A0engage with a bidder, Weinstein, who=C2=A0<em>is=C2=A0</=
em>in the hedge-fund-managing business, and who would not keep Levin around=
.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">And then when Weinstein offered =
a higher price anyway, Sculptor brushed him off, saying that his deal was t=
oo contingent, and refusing to negotiate with him to firm it up.</li>
</ul>
