<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">You could tell a nicer version of this story. =
The nicer version goes like this:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Sculptor=E2=80=99s=C2=A0<em>clients=C2=
=A0</em>=E2=80=94=C2=A0the limited partners in its hedge funds, whose money=
