t; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[4]</span>
</a> When it started discussions with potential buyers, it told management =
=E2=80=9Cthat the Company=E2=80=99s management would not be permitted to en=
gage in any negotiations with any prospective counterparties to a potential=
