o be $11.15 per share from Rithm.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In Sculptor=E2=80=99s story, the problem is ju=
st that the Weinstein group never made a real bid. Weinstein <em>was=C2=A0<=
/em>part of the auction process, but his bid was lower than Rithm=E2=80=99s=
