nd they could=C2=A0walk away by paying a $19.6 million breakup fee. The spe=
cial committee would rather get $11.15 per share of fairly certain cash fro=
m Rithm than roll the dice on getting $12.25 from Weinstein and perhaps hav=
ing the deal fall apart.</p>
