ound-color: #ccc;">  David Solomon</a>, =E2=80=9Ca rare executive atop Gold=
man who already had a thriving career before he made his way to the Wall St=
reet giant in 1999.=E2=80=9D We have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
