contemplating selling the company, should you consider *only* maximizing th=
e price you get for shareholders of the management company, or *also* doing=
 what is right for the investors in the fund? If, like, Elon Musk came alon=
g and offered Sculptor an ironclad deal to pay $13 per share, and announced=
