 that offer? Incidentally the big private-equity firms that went public oft=
en <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32465527.261426=
/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTUtMDItMDEvYmxhY2=
tzdG9uZS1zLXNjaHdhcnptYW4tc2F5cy1kdXR5LWlzbi10LXRvLXB1YmxpYy1zaGFyZWhvbGRlc=
